<title type="html"><![CDATA[8/21(Sun.) Street Food (Introduction of Asia) / Why is everyone so bad at giving gifts? (Host: Jennie)]]></title>

<content type="html" xml:base="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/viewtopic.php?t=645&amp;p=670#p670"><![CDATA[
8/21(Sun.) Street Food (Introduction of Asia) / Why is everyone so bad at giving gifts? (Host: Jennie)<br /><br />Agenda:<br />7:00-7:05 pm Opening Remarks<br />7:05-7:40 pm Session 1: Group Discussion<br />7:40-8:00 pm Individual Presentation<br />8:00-8:05 pm Break<br />8:05-8:35 pm Session 2: Group Discussion<br />8:35-9:00 pm Debate<br /><br />We will hold a zoom meeting only.<br /><br />Zoom meeting: Please click the link below<br /><br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://zoomtw.zoom.us/j/92987266213?pw">https://zoomtw.zoom.us/j/92987266213?pw</a><!-- m --> ...<br />Meeting ID:929 8726 6213<br />Password:112233<br /><br />--------------------------------------------<br /><br />Session I: Street Food (Introduction of Asia)<br /><br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://youtu.be/eI_LjETc_Ak">https://youtu.be/eI_LjETc_Ak</a><!-- m --><br /><br />Questions:<br />1. Do you like the culture of street food? Why yes or why not?<br /><br />2.In Taiwan, what are the favorites of street food you just can’t resist?<br /><br />3.When you travel abroad, would you like to try the local street food? If any, please share with us your unforgettable cuisine.<br /><br />4. What kind of Taiwanese street food will you introduce to your friends from overseas? Such as “stinky fried tofu”, ”pig blood cake”, “preserved egg with tofu”“.<br /><br />---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />Session II: Why is everyone so bad at giving gifts?<br /><br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://youtu.be/Q9UUu2JBQB0">https://youtu.be/Q9UUu2JBQB0</a><!-- m --><br /><br />Questions:<br />1. What is the worst holiday gift you’ve ever received?                                                         <br />  <br />2. Do you usually consider the desirability or feasibility while giving a gift?                <br /><br />3. Do you think that giving cash is a more practical idea? <br /><br />4. As a gift giver, will you directly ask the recipients what they want? As a recipient, will you tell the gift giver what you ask for?                                                  Please share us with your experience if any.<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=46353">Ellen Lu</a> — Wed Aug 17, 2022 9:36 pm</p><hr />
